close_reason: "Comprehensive dogfood audit complete: 1052/1052 tests pass, all CLI features verified in sandbox, telemetry stack operational with [redacted_event_count] events, SDK and calendar reviewed, 3 new issues created (pm-gusd, pm-pxx0, pm-wsui), existing tracking items updated with audit evidence, test robustness fix applied to telemetry-runtime.spec.ts"
body: "Comprehensive dogfood audit of the entire pm CLI conducted in a sandboxed temporary project. All CLI features verified, SDK reviewed, calendar tested, telemetry pipeline validated end-to-end, remote stack confirmed operational."
